INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 100, 0, "Thank you all for attending this sermon. It's wonderful to see so many familiar faces!", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 101, 0, "Today I would like to touch on the three virtues of the Light.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 102, 0, "These are dark and difficult times for us all. The armies of the Scourge amass to the south. Companions fall on the battlefield and rise to serve our enemy moments later.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 103, 0, "Many of you have experienced a betrayal of trust.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 104, 0, "Yet you persevere, as we all must. In these times, no one is a stranger to the virtue of tenacity. In the face of despair and hatred, we continue to stand true to our beliefs and fight on.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 105, 0, "There can be no doubt as to your tenacity... but there are other virtues to consider.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 106, 0, "Respect is the first virtue taught to those joining the path of the Light.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 107, 0, "Look across the aisle to those you would call enemy. Despite the hatred that separates you, there are qualities to respect in your opponent. Their prowess should be acknowledged.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 108, 0, "All of us gathered here have a concept of honorable combat. Conducting yourself with honor and treating your opponent as you wish to be treated shows respect.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 109, 0, "Respect your opponent on the field, whether he be your brother or your sworn enemy. No matter where your beliefs truly lie, such respect is acknowledging a connection...", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 110, 0, "...and in acknowledging those connections, you are closer to the Light.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 111, 0, "There is one further step on the path of Light: compassion.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 112, 0, "Rivalries abound in this day and age. It is easy to see differences wherever you turn.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 113, 0, "The challenge is in looking beyond appearances and understanding our similarities. Through this understanding, you can feel compassion for the losses others have suffered...", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 114, 0, "...even if the victim bears another banner.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 115, 0, "By feeling and understanding compassion in enemy and ally alike, you reaffirm your connection with the world.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 116, 0, "Acting on these tenets, these virtues, help make the world a place we all can appreciate. A world of honor and justice.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 117, 0, "Think on my words, friends. In the darkness that surrounds us all, the Light is needed more than ever.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 118, 0, "I'll be behind the confessional screen if anyone wishes to speak with me. Any doubts, any worries, any uncertainties I will happily soothe.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (33462, 0, 0, "I don't know if I can compete! Everyone is so much bigger!", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Gnomeregan Champion");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (33462, 1, 0, "I've calculated the probability of my success, and it's distressingly low!", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Gnomeregan Champion");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (33462, 2, 0, "I can't accurately assess the mathematics behind the charge of my turbostrider while keeping hold of my lance at the precise angle needed and keeping my shield in the exact location for maximum protection at any given second!", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Gnomeregan Champion");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (33462, 3, 0, "...and some of those mounts can trample me!", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Gnomeregan Champion");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 0, 0, "Take heart. Size isn't what matters, but how you use the skills you have.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
INSERT INTO creature_text VALUES (34102, 1, 0, "What you lack in size you make up for in ambition and dedication, little one. Go with the Light.", 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, "Argent Confessor Paletress");
